This product includes work derived from and informed by the following projects:

1. Chuffnugget/volcano_integration  (MIT License, Copyright (c) 2025 Chuffnugget)
   https://github.com/Chuffnugget/volcano_integration
   The Volcano Hybrid BLE connection, read/write, and notification handling in
   custom_components/storz_bickel/api/devices/volcano.py were adapted from this
   project's bluetooth_coordinator.py, reworked to use Home Assistant's
   bleak-retry-connector connection management and this project's device
   abstraction.

   The MIT License text from the upstream project is reproduced below.

2. firsttris/reactive-volcano-app  (no published license — used as a protocol reference only)
   https://github.com/firsttris/reactive-volcano-app
   The reverse-engineered GATT service/characteristic UUIDs, byte layouts, command
   opcodes, and bit masks for the Volcano, Venty, Veazy, and Crafty devices were
   used as a protocol specification. No source code from this project was copied;
   the parsing logic in custom_components/storz_bickel/api/ is an original Python
   implementation.

